{"id":641510,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/【网络民议】他们不爱自己的国王-也不爱自己的/","date":"2020-04-13T07:55:12Z","modified":"2020-04-14T09:05:52Z","title":"【网络民议】“他们居然不爱自己的国王 也不爱自己的政府”","content":"<p>近日，泰国男星Bright及女友Weetaya意外“辱华”，激怒大量中国爱国网友翻墙远征，掀起“中泰键盘战”。对于这场“中泰键盘战”的起因，据媒体报道主要由Bright的女友Weetaya提及“武汉肺炎”和“台湾”所引发：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_641570\" style=\"width: 650px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/640_a185e7cd04a9871f2979678c4c863015.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641570\" class=\"size-full wp-image-641570\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/640_a185e7cd04a9871f2979678c4c863015.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/640_a185e7cd04a9871f2979678c4c863015.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/640_a185e7cd04a9871f2979678c4c863015-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641570\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bright及女友Weetaya</p></div>\n<blockquote><p><strong>三立新闻网｜泰国网友「帮台湾独立」！中国网军震怒：即日起不翻译泰剧</strong></p>\n<p>泰国BL剧《因为我们天生一对》（2gether: The Series／中国译：假偶天成）广受观众喜爱，演员们也因此开启知名度，没想到近日男主角之一的Bright却因替戏外女友一篇转发「武汉肺炎」的贴文点赞，拨动到中国网友的敏感神经，翻出2人过往的贴文，直说他们「辱华」。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_641513\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7828daf16f62450a904a7e5a44eb25a3.jpeg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641513\" class=\"wp-image-641513\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7828daf16f62450a904a7e5a44eb25a3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7828daf16f62450a904a7e5a44eb25a3.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7828daf16f62450a904a7e5a44eb25a3-174x300.jpeg 174w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641513\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bright女友Weetaya所转发的推文</p></div>\n<p>这波「中泰大战」起因Bright女友Weetaya（IG帐号为nnevvy）在推特转发了武汉肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）相关文章，而Bright点赞，立刻挑起中国的敏感神经，开始挖出小俩口过往互动，发现Weetaya在2年前曾对于男友留言赞美他「真好看像个中国女孩」时满头问号，却在被网友询问穿着风格时回答是「是台湾女孩喔」，被中国网军直指台独，要求Bright和Weetaya为此道歉。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/BB12uzjG.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641511\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/BB12uzjG.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"865\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/BB12uzjG.jpg 259w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/BB12uzjG-139x300.jpg 139w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在这场“中泰骂战”中，中方爱国网友发布的内容以组队灌水、批评泰国王室及政府、抵制泰剧等为主。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_641514\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641514\" class=\"wp-image-641514\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"595\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民.jpg 728w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民-252x300.jpg 252w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641514\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">泰国国家旅游局微博下的网民评论</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_641517\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVZjFYcUEAANsSM.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641517\" class=\"wp-image-641517\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVZjFYcUEAANsSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVZjFYcUEAANsSM.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVZjFYcUEAANsSM-300x211.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641517\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">有中国网友以PS泰国王室成员的方式回击</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_641515\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民2-7.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641515\" class=\"wp-image-641515\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民2-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民2-7.jpg 747w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/泰国网民2-7-300x196.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641515\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">@天府泰剧 宣布停止对《只因我们天生一对》的停更</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p>@Bibinibi3：泰国南波湾！！泰国，不能让女性堕胎。泰国，国王一夫多妻。泰国，妄议国王要被抓起来。泰国，虐待动物。泰国，被欧洲美国看不起却很骄傲。泰国，存在着剥削女性的王室，册封还得下跪，还活在200年以前吧。泰国。总理外逃。泰国人不了解外面的世界，却总以为自己很厉害，一个被洗脑的国家。萨瓦迪卡</p>\n<p>@Bea98304066：说实话，bright和他女友怎么样，我都不在乎，这是他们的隐私，I dont care.但是，为什么要把事情搞这么大呢？台湾本来就是中国的。如果一定要打着自由言论的旗号用台湾问题来戳中国刀子干涉中国内政的话，那我是不是可以理解为我也可以说泰国和柬埔寨领土问题，泰国政治和王室的问题</p>\n<p>@naiki60793582：现在都2020年了，一个还要向王室下跪，国王能取娶十几个妃子，王妃随意被废死在监狱的国家，有什么资格跟中国谈民主自由人权？泰国多大脸？</p>\n<p>@zhouyue66248126：#ChinaHongKong和Taiwan一直都是我们中国的中国旗帜，你们不承认也没办法，这是不争的事实，希望你们港独和台独想清楚，泰国人民就不要插手中国内政，一个靠旅游业发展的国家，泰国旅游业基本上都是中国百姓贡献的，得罪了中国，你们的经济会受损的，希望你们想清楚。</p>\n<p>@Alex31299146：泰国人你们真是傻逼 活该穷死。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVVv0gEUMAA23Sf.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-641516\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVVv0gEUMAA23Sf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"360\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVVv0gEUMAA23Sf.jpg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVVv0gEUMAA23Sf-300x293.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVVv0gEUMAA23Sf-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>而不少泰国网友在推特上以 #nnevvy 为tag（Weetaya的帐号名），发表大量辱包、支持台湾香港独立、讽刺中国缺乏自由等内容回击，同时制作了大量的网络表情包。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_641519\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVbYu6LVAAAJWO0.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641519\" class=\"wp-image-641519\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVbYu6LVAAAJWO0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVbYu6LVAAAJWO0.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVbYu6LVAAAJWO0-300x148.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641519\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">动物们都走了 —— 习近平</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_641520\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdwxWRUYAE00kw.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641520\" class=\"wp-image-641520\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdwxWRUYAE00kw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"583\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdwxWRUYAE00kw.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdwxWRUYAE00kw-257x300.jpg 257w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641520\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">泰国网友表情包 支持台湾香港</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_641518\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641518\" class=\"wp-image-641518\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios-183x300.jpg 183w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios-624x1024.jpg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios-768x1260.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/image_from_ios-936x1536.jpg 936w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641518\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">泰国网民的反击：笼的传人</p></div>\n<p>由于不少爱国网民频繁使用国骂NMSL、CNMB，导致这些词汇很快被泰国网友习得含义，以“NMSLESE ”等自创词汇反击，与反送中运动中期间出现的“CHINAZI”颇有相似。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVa8k55XkAARuF0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641521\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVa8k55XkAARuF0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"496\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVa8k55XkAARuF0.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVa8k55XkAARuF0-300x298.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVa8k55XkAARuF0-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVa8k55XkAARuF0-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdSi2gUYAAQeyf.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641522 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdSi2gUYAAQeyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"504\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdSi2gUYAAQeyf.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdSi2gUYAAQeyf-298x300.jpg 298w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdSi2gUYAAQeyf-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVdSi2gUYAAQeyf-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"ElNGuAW3F6\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/%e3%80%90%e7%9b%9b%e4%b8%96%e4%b8%80%e6%99%af%e3%80%91%e8%b5%a4%e7%ba%b3%e7%b2%b9%e6%97%97%ef%bc%88chinazi-flag%ef%bc%89/\">【盛世一景】赤纳粹旗（ChiNazi flag）</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【盛世一景】赤纳粹旗（ChiNazi flag）》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/%e3%80%90%e7%9b%9b%e4%b8%96%e4%b8%80%e6%99%af%e3%80%91%e8%b5%a4%e7%ba%b3%e7%b2%b9%e6%97%97%ef%bc%88chinazi-flag%ef%bc%89/embed/#?secret=ElNGuAW3F6\" data-secret=\"ElNGuAW3F6\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>正当这场骂战如火如荼之际，有中国爱国网民基于对不自由生活的体验，以及对泰国政治生态、网络社群构成的不了解，开始发布辱骂泰国王室和泰国政府的言论，希望以此激怒泰国网民。未料大量对王室及政府持负面看法的泰国网民纷纷要求“请继续”、“大声点”，导致这波中方攻击落入笑柄。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Thank you thailand warriors, love thais <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nnevvy?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#nnevvy</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/xfBnVE9YHM\">pic.twitter.com/xfBnVE9YHM</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Yan (@lyt_55) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lyt_55/status/1249477720016171008?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 12, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Wumao: trying their best to get a stable VPN connection &amp; hurl abuse at Thai ppl.<br />Thai: Noted with thanks. Try harder<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nnevvy?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#nnevvy</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/TeamThailand?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#TeamThailand</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/cBy6pzmwyD\">pic.twitter.com/cBy6pzmwyD</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Bruce😷 #StayHomeSaveLives (@BruceWayne852) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BruceWayne852/status/1249389624029360129?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 12, 2020</a></p></